Games-Solitaire-BlackHole-Solver

This is a solver for the Solitaire "Black Hole", implemented in Perl as a
command line application. See:

http://pysolfc.sourceforge.net/doc/rules/blackhole.html

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Build.PL
	./Build
	./Build test
	./Build install

SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the
perldoc command.

    perldoc Games::Solitaire::BlackHole::Solver

You can also look for information at:

    RT, CPAN's request tracker
        http://rt.cpan.org/NoAuth/Bugs.html?Dist=Games-Solitaire-BlackHole-Solver

    AnnoCPAN, Annotated CPAN documentation
        http://annocpan.org/dist/Games-Solitaire-BlackHole-Solver

    CPAN Ratings
        http://cpanratings.perl.org/d/Games-Solitaire-BlackHole-Solver

    Search CPAN
        http://search.cpan.org/dist/Games-Solitaire-BlackHole-Solver/


